BOOLEAN RtStreamingEndPoint::Open (  RtStreamingConn &  conn  ) 
 

Opens an endpoint and associates it with a streaming connection.

Parameters:
conn Connection to associate with the current endpoint.
Calls OnOpen() to prepare the data source / sink. When OnOpen() returns 'TRUE' the endpoint is attached to the connection.
